OL,3,CDouglas Ross to quit as Scottish Tory
OL,4,Cleader after general election
OL,6,FFirst Minister John Swinney has
OL,7,Faccused Scottish Tory leader Douglas
OL,8,FRoss of treating voters with contempt
OL,9,F` after the Conservative announced he
OL,10,Fwould only quit Holyrood if he wins a
OL,11,Fseat at Westminster.
OL,13,FThe leader of the Conservatives has
OL,14,Fsaid he will stand down after the
OL,15,FGeneral Election and will also quit
OL,16,FHolyrood .
OL,18,FDouglas Ross made the announcement in
OL,19,Fthe wake of the row over his decision
OL,20,Fto stand in the Aberdeen North and
OL,21,FMoray East constituency.
