OL,3,CDouglas Ross to quit as Scottish Tory
OL,4,Cleader after general election
OL,6,FIn a statement released on Monday, Mr
OL,7,FRoss said: "I am committed to fighting
OL,8,Fand winning the Aberdeenshire North
OL,9,Fand Moray East constituency.
OL,11,F"Should I be given the honour to
OL,12,Frepresent the people and communities
OL,13,Fof this new seat, they should know
OL,14,Fbeing their MP would receive my
OL,15,Fcomplete focus and attention.
OL,17,F"I will therefore stand down as leader
OL,18,Ffollowing the election on July 4, once
OL,19,Fa successor is elected.
