OL,3,CDouglas Ross to quit as Scottish Tory
OL,4,Cleader after general election
OL,6,F"Should I win the seat, I will also
OL,7,Fstand down as an MSP to make way for
OL,8,Fanother Scottish Conservative
OL,9,Frepresentative in Holyrood."
OL,11,FHe insisted: "My party has a chance to
OL,12,Fbeat the SNP in key seats up and down
OL,13,FScotland, including in Aberdeenshire
OL,14,FNorth and Moray East. We must now come
OL,15,Ftogether and fully focus on doing
OL,16,Fexactly that."
